name: Car Listing
description: This is a mobile application that lists various cars on the screen. Details included are rating, pros/cons, MSRP, etc. The app also includes options for sorting and filtering.

name: Cat Platformer
description: This is a basic platforming game, using a cat as a player. Accumulate points by collecting fish, and battle the evil rat enemy. Development in progress.

name: Chore Chart
description: This is a mobile app for logging chores and rewards for a household. The app uses the google firestore database for storing people, chores, and rewards.

name: Basic Drawing
description: This is a basic drawing mobile application. You can draw in different thicknesses, shapes, and colors. The app also allows for undo and redo of lines drawn.

name: Garden Plot Planner
description: A console application garden plot planner in C#. You can choose the size of your garden plot, add/remove plants, and load plants from a file.

name: Goal Manager
description: This is a goal manager console application in C#.

name: Chamber Site
description: This is a practice chamber of commerce website. Pages include a home page, discover page, directory page, and a join form. Website is made interactive using JavaScript, and styled using CSS.

name: Portfolio
description: It's this site. It is a portfolio showcasing my programming projects.
